### MongoDB Classify Endpoints
# These endpoints provide paginated access to classifications with various filters

# --- Variables ---
@host = http://localhost:8000
@api_key = your_api_key_here
@auth_token = Bearer {{api_key}}

### Get Recent Classifications (Page 1)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/mongo/classify/recent?page=1
Authorization: {{auth_token}}

### Get Recent Classifications (Page 2)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/mongo/classify/recent?page=2
Authorization: {{auth_token}}

### Get Oldest Classifications (Page 1)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/mongo/classify/oldest?page=1
Authorization: {{auth_token}}

### Get Successful Classifications (Page 1)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/mongo/classify/successful?page=1
Authorization: {{auth_token}}

### Get Failed Classifications (Page 1)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/mongo/classify/failed?page=1
Authorization: {{auth_token}}

### Get Disqualified Classifications (Page 1)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/mongo/classify/disqualified?page=1
Authorization: {{auth_token}}

### Get Classifications by Lead Type - Services (Page 1)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/mongo/classify/by-lead-type?lead_type=Services&page=1
Authorization: {{auth_token}}

### Get Classifications by Lead Type - Logistics (Page 1)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/mongo/classify/by-lead-type?lead_type=Logistics&page=1
Authorization: {{auth_token}}

### Get Classifications by Lead Type - Leads (Page 1)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/mongo/classify/by-lead-type?lead_type=Leads&page=1
Authorization: {{auth_token}}

### Get Classifications by Confidence Level - High (Page 1)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/mongo/classify/by-confidence?min_confidence=0.8&page=1
Authorization: {{auth_token}}

### Get Classifications by Confidence Level - Medium (Page 1)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/mongo/classify/by-confidence?min_confidence=0.5&page=1
Authorization: {{auth_token}}

### Get Classifications by Confidence Level - Low (Page 1)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/mongo/classify/by-confidence?min_confidence=0.1&page=1
Authorization: {{auth_token}}

### Get Classifications by Source - WebForm (Page 1)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/mongo/classify/by-source?source=webform&page=1
Authorization: {{auth_token}}

### Get Classifications by Source - Voice (Page 1)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/mongo/classify/by-source?source=voice&page=1
Authorization: {{auth_token}}

### Get Classifications by Source - Email (Page 1)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/mongo/classify/by-source?source=email&page=1
Authorization: {{auth_token}}

### Get Classification by ID
GET {{host}}/api/v1/mongo/classify/classification_id_here
Authorization: {{auth_token}}

### Sample Classification ID lookup
GET {{host}}/api/v1/mongo/classify/67890abcdef1234567890abc
Authorization: {{auth_token}}
